2.1. Grants
We hereby grant You a world-wide, royalty-free, non-exclusive license to

a. distribute copies of the Executable Form pre-loaded on Your Firefox OS
Devices for the purpose of making those Firefox OS Devices ACL-Ready, and

b. reproduce copies of the Source Code Form for Your company's internal
use only, where the number of such copies is limited to that reasonably
necessary for You to make the copies of the Executable Form for
distribution per Section 2.1.a.
We hereby grant to end users of Your Firefox OS Devices a world-wide,
royalty-free, non-exclusive license to use copies of the Executable Form
pre-loaded on those devices by you.

2.2. Effective Date
This License is effective as of the earliest of Your indicating
acceptance of the terms of this License via (i) Our automated licensing
portal at https://manager.openmobileappmall.com/gsl_partner_signup.php,
and (ii) Your downloading the Source Code Form (along with this License)
